<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= title %> – Kishore Orthopedic Centre</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <main>
    <!-- Hero with background image -->
    <section class="page-hero page-hero--image" style="background-image: url('/images/arthroscopy.jpg')">
      <div class="page-hero__overlay"></div>
      <div class="container page-hero__content">
        <span class="section-tag section-tag--light">What We Offer</span>
        <h1>Our Treatments &amp; Services</h1>
        <p>A full spectrum of orthopedic care — from precision surgery and advanced trauma management to rehabilitation and pain relief.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Treatments Section -->
    <section class="section treatments-section">
      <div class="container">

        <!-- Filter Tabs -->
        <div class="treatment-tabs">
          <button class="tab-btn active" data-tab="all">All Treatments</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="surgical">Surgical</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="non-surgical">Non-Surgical</button>
          <button class="tab-btn" data-tab="rehab">Rehabilitation</button>
        </div>

        <!-- Category Label: Surgical -->
        <div class="category-divider category-divider--surgical" data-show-for="surgical all">
          <span class="category-divider__label">Surgical Treatments</span>
          <div class="category-divider__line"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="treatments-grid" id="treatmentsGrid">

          <!-- Spine Surgery -->
          <div class="treatment-card" data-category="surgical">
            <div class="treatment-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/spine.jpg" alt="Spine Surgery" class="treatment-img" />
              <span class="treatment-category treatment-category--surgical">Surgical</span>
            </div>
            <div class="treatment-body">
              <h3>Spine Surgery</h3>
              <p>Comprehensive surgical solutions for disc herniations, spinal stenosis, deformities and instability. Fellowship-trained in Switzerland for complex spinal conditions.</p>
              <ul class="treatment-points">
                <li>Discectomy &amp; Laminectomy</li>
                <li>Spinal Fusion &amp; Fixation</li>
                <li>Scoliosis Correction</li>
                <li>Minimally Invasive Spine Procedures</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Contact Clinic</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Joint Replacements -->
          <div class="treatment-card" data-category="surgical">
            <div class="treatment-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/joint-replacement.jpg" alt="Joint Replacement Surgery" class="treatment-img" />
              <span class="treatment-category treatment-category--surgical">Surgical</span>
            </div>
            <div class="treatment-body">
              <h3>Joint Replacements</h3>
              <p>Advanced knee, hip and shoulder replacement surgeries to relieve severe arthritis pain and restore full mobility using precision implant techniques.</p>
              <ul class="treatment-points">
                <li>Total &amp; Partial Knee Replacement</li>
                <li>Total Hip Replacement</li>
                <li>Shoulder Replacement</li>
                <li>Minimally Invasive Approach</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Contact Clinic</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Arthroscopy -->
          <div class="treatment-card" data-category="surgical">
            <div class="treatment-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/arthroscopy.jpg" alt="Arthroscopy Surgery" class="treatment-img" />
              <span class="treatment-category treatment-category--surgical">Surgical</span>
            </div>
            <div class="treatment-body">
              <h3>Arthroscopy</h3>
              <p>Minimally invasive keyhole surgery for diagnosing and treating problems inside joints — smaller incisions, less pain and faster recovery compared to open surgery.</p>
              <ul class="treatment-points">
                <li>Knee Arthroscopy &amp; Meniscus Repair</li>
                <li>ACL / PCL Reconstruction</li>
                <li>Shoulder Arthroscopy</li>
                <li>Hip Arthroscopy</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Contact Clinic</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Ilizarov & Limb Reconstruction -->
          <div class="treatment-card" data-category="surgical">
            <div class="treatment-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/ilizarov.jpg" alt="Ilizarov & Limb Reconstruction" class="treatment-img treatment-img--contain" />
              <span class="treatment-category treatment-category--surgical">Surgical</span>
            </div>
            <div class="treatment-body">
              <h3>Ilizarov &amp; Limb Reconstruction</h3>
              <p>Specialised limb reconstruction surgery using the Ilizarov method — fellowship trained in Kurgan, Russia. Used for limb lengthening, deformity correction and bone reconstruction.</p>
              <ul class="treatment-points">
                <li>Limb Lengthening</li>
                <li>Bone Deformity Correction</li>
                <li>Non-Union Fracture Treatment</li>
                <li>Complex Limb Salvage</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Contact Clinic</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Limb Lengthening -->
          <div class="treatment-card" data-category="surgical">
            <div class="treatment-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/limb-lengthening.jpg" alt="Limb Lengthening Surgery" class="treatment-img" />
              <span class="treatment-category treatment-category--surgical">Surgical</span>
            </div>
            <div class="treatment-body">
              <h3>Limb Lengthening</h3>
              <p>Advanced limb lengthening procedures for correcting limb length discrepancies and short stature. Using the Ilizarov and other modern techniques, gradual bone regeneration achieves precise, controlled lengthening.</p>
              <ul class="treatment-points">
                <li>Ilizarov Limb Lengthening</li>
                <li>Limb Length Discrepancy Correction</li>
                <li>Short Stature Management</li>
                <li>Post-Lengthening Rehabilitation</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Contact Clinic</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Flap Coverage -->
          <div class="treatment-card" data-category="surgical">
            <div class="treatment-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/flap-coverage.jpg" alt="Flap Coverage for Open Wounds" class="treatment-img" />
              <span class="treatment-category treatment-category--surgical">Surgical</span>
            </div>
            <div class="treatment-body">
              <h3>Flap Coverage for Open Wounds</h3>
              <p>Surgical wound coverage techniques for complex open fractures and soft tissue defects. Ensures proper healing of exposed bone, tendons and joints through advanced plastic and reconstructive procedures.</p>
              <ul class="treatment-points">
                <li>Rotational Flap Procedures</li>
                <li>Free Flap Microsurgery</li>
                <li>Wound Debridement &amp; Management</li>
                <li>Post-Trauma Reconstruction</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Contact Clinic</a>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div><!-- end surgical grid -->

        <!-- Category Label: Non-Surgical -->
        <div class="category-divider category-divider--nonsurgical" data-show-for="non-surgical all">
          <span class="category-divider__label">Non-Surgical Treatments</span>
          <div class="category-divider__line"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="treatments-grid treatments-grid--nonsurgical" id="nonSurgicalGrid">

          <!-- Trauma Care -->
          <div class="treatment-card" data-category="non-surgical">
            <div class="treatment-img-wrap treatment-img-wrap--gradient">
              <div class="treatment-img-placeholder">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="52" height="52">
                  <circle cx="32" cy="32" r="30" stroke="#0369a1" stroke-width="2.5" fill="none"/>
                  <path d="M32 18v14M32 42v2" stroke="#0369a1" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                  <path d="M22 26l10 6 10-6" stroke="#0ea5e9" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                </svg>
                <span>Emergency &amp; Trauma</span>
              </div>
              <span class="treatment-category treatment-category--nonsurgical">Non-Surgical</span>
            </div>
            <div class="treatment-body">
              <h3>Trauma Care</h3>
              <p>Comprehensive emergency orthopedic management for fractures, dislocations and acute musculoskeletal injuries — available 24 hours, 7 days a week.</p>
              <ul class="treatment-points">
                <li>Emergency Fracture Management</li>
                <li>Dislocation Reduction</li>
                <li>Cast &amp; Splint Application</li>
                <li>Poly-Trauma Assessment</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Contact Clinic</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Rheumatology -->
          <div class="treatment-card" data-category="non-surgical">
            <div class="treatment-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/rheumatology.jpg" alt="Rheumatology Treatment" class="treatment-img" />
              <span class="treatment-category treatment-category--nonsurgical">Non-Surgical</span>
            </div>
            <div class="treatment-body">
              <h3>Rheumatology</h3>
              <p>Medical management of inflammatory joint conditions including rheumatoid arthritis, ankylosing spondylitis and gout — focused on pain control and preserving joint function.</p>
              <ul class="treatment-points">
                <li>Rheumatoid Arthritis Management</li>
                <li>Ankylosing Spondylitis Care</li>
                <li>Gout &amp; Crystal Arthropathies</li>
                <li>Injection Therapy for Joints</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Contact Clinic</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Polio & Cerebral Palsy -->
          <div class="treatment-card" data-category="non-surgical">
            <div class="treatment-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/polio-cerebral-palsy.jpg" alt="Polio & Cerebral Palsy Care" class="treatment-img treatment-img--top" />
              <span class="treatment-category treatment-category--nonsurgical">Non-Surgical</span>
            </div>
            <div class="treatment-body">
              <h3>Polio &amp; Cerebral Palsy</h3>
              <p>Specialised orthopedic care for children and adults with polio sequelae and cerebral palsy. Improving mobility, correcting deformities and enhancing quality of life through targeted interventions.</p>
              <ul class="treatment-points">
                <li>Deformity Correction</li>
                <li>Orthotic &amp; Bracing Support</li>
                <li>Tendon Transfer Procedures</li>
                <li>Physiotherapy Integration</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Contact Clinic</a>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div><!-- end non-surgical grid -->

        <!-- Category Label: Rehabilitation -->
        <div class="category-divider category-divider--rehab" data-show-for="rehab all">
          <span class="category-divider__label">Rehabilitation &amp; Physiotherapy</span>
          <div class="category-divider__line"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="treatments-grid treatments-grid--rehab" id="rehabGrid">

          <!-- Physiotherapy -->
          <div class="treatment-card treatment-card--wide" data-category="rehab">
            <div class="treatment-img-wrap">
              <img src="/images/physiotherapy.jpg" alt="Physiotherapy" class="treatment-img" />
              <span class="treatment-category treatment-category--rehab">Rehabilitation</span>
            </div>
            <div class="treatment-body">
              <h3>Physiotherapy &amp; Rehabilitation</h3>
              <p>Expert, structured physiotherapy programmes designed to restore strength, mobility and function after surgery, injury or chronic conditions. Our rehabilitation team works closely with Dr. Kishore Kumar to ensure seamless care from surgery to full recovery.</p>
              <ul class="treatment-points">
                <li>Post-Surgical Rehabilitation</li>
                <li>Manual &amp; Manipulative Therapy</li>
                <li>Electrotherapy (TENS, Ultrasound)</li>
                <li>Gait Retraining &amp; Balance</li>
                <li>Sports Rehabilitation &amp; Return-to-Sport</li>
              </ul>
              <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">Contact Clinic</a>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div><!-- end rehab grid -->

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Surgical Expertise Showcase -->
    <section class="section section-alt surgical-expertise">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="expertise-inner">
          <div class="expertise-content">
            <span class="section-tag">In the Operating Room</span>
            <h2>International-Standard Surgical Expertise</h2>
            <p>Dr. M. Kishore Kumar brings internationally trained surgical skill to every procedure. With fellowships from Switzerland and Russia alongside advanced training in joint replacement and arthroscopy, every surgery is performed with precision, safety and care.</p>
            <ul class="expertise-list">
              <li>
                <div class="expertise-icon">✓</div>
                <span>Fellowship-trained in Spine Surgery (Switzerland)</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="expertise-icon">✓</div>
                <span>Ilizarov training from Kurgan, Russia — a world centre for limb reconstruction</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="expertise-icon">✓</div>
                <span>Advanced Arthroscopy &amp; Joint Replacement techniques</span>
              </li>
              <li>
                <div class="expertise-icon">✓</div>
                <span>State-of-the-art operation theatre with modern equipment</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <div class="expertise-actions">
              <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Clinic</a>
              <a href="https://wa.me/917093571238" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-whatsapp">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="16" height="16"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
                WhatsApp Inquiry
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="expertise-image">
            <img src="/images/surgery.png" alt="Dr. M. Kishore Kumar performing surgery" class="expertise-img" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How It Works -->
    <section class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-header">
          <span class="section-tag">Your Journey With Us</span>
          <h2>How It Works</h2>
          <p>A clear, caring process from first consultation to full recovery.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="process-steps">
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">01</div>
            <h3>Consultation</h3>
            <p>Meet Dr. Kishore Kumar for a thorough assessment of your condition, medical history and goals.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step-arrow">→</div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">02</div>
            <h3>Diagnosis</h3>
            <p>Advanced imaging (X-ray, MRI, CT) and clinical evaluation to pinpoint the exact problem.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step-arrow">→</div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">03</div>
            <h3>Treatment Plan</h3>
            <p>A personalised, evidence-based plan tailored to your condition, lifestyle and recovery goals.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="step-arrow">→</div>
          <div class="step">
            <div class="step-number">04</div>
            <h3>Recovery</h3>
            <p>Supported rehabilitation with regular follow-ups until you're back to your best.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
